name: El Nacimiento
description:
This exquisite piece embraces the deep and perfect love
between a mother and her child. The mother's love is so
strong that it is able to protect her child from any danger,
no matter how great. The child's love is so pure that it
returns the love of the mother unconditionally. Together.
